# identity service

Module: `github.com/sedorofeevd/project-druzya/services/identity`. Work from service root only.

## Layers

```
cmd/identity/app/run.go       → DI
internal/app/api/identity/    → gRPC/HTTP transport
internal/user/                → user model + postgres repository
internal/auth/                → auth model + redis repository + service
internal/adapter/yandex/      → external OAuth client
```

## Dev

`make start` | `make run` | `make lint` | `make gen-proto`

HTTP `:8080`, gRPC `:9090`. See `AGENTS.md`.
